## Component Specifications

### 1. Navigation Bar (Desktop)
```
Layout: Flex, justify-between, items-center
Height: 52px
Background: White with subtle shadow

Left Section:
- Logo (custom)
- Search bar with icon (expandable on mobile)
  - Placeholder: "Search"
  - Background: #EEF3F8
  - Border-radius: 4px
  - Focus: blue border

Right Section (Icon + Label, vertical stack):
- Home (house icon) - active state: black icon, blue underline
- My Network (people icon)
- Jobs (briefcase icon)
- Messaging (chat icon) - show unread count badge
- Notifications (bell icon) - show count badge
- Profile dropdown:
  - Avatar (32x32, circular)
  - "Me" label with dropdown arrow
  - Dropdown menu: View Profile, Settings, Sign Out

Navigation Items:
- Icon size: 24px
- Label: 12px, text-secondary
- Active: blue bottom border (3px)
- Hover: subtle gray background
```

### 2. Mobile Bottom Navigation
```
Position: Fixed bottom
Height: 50px
Background: White
Border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0
Display: 5 equal-width items

Items: Home, Network, Post (+), Notifications, Jobs
- Center item (Post): Highlighted with blue background, white icon
- Active state: Blue icon color
- Inactive: Gray icon
```

### 3. Left Sidebar - Profile Card
```
Card with:
- Cover image placeholder (60px height, gradient background)
- Profile avatar (72px, circular, positioned -36px from cover)
- Name (16px, bold, clickable)
- Headline (14px, text-secondary, 2 lines max)
- Divider
- Stats section:
  - "Profile viewers: 45" (clickable)
  - "Post impressions: 234" (clickable)
- Divider
- "My items" section (saved posts, etc.)
```

